ass=\"centre-of-competence-in-aerospace-history centres-of-competence\"><a href=\"http://www.alr-aerospace.ch/index.php?id=centre-of-competence-in-aerospace-history\" title=\"Centre of Competence in Aerospace History\">Aerospace History</a></li>\n</ul></li>\n<li class=\"reference-projects\"><a href=\"http://www.alr-aerospace.ch/index.php?id=reference-projects\" title=\"Reference Projects\">Reference Projects</a></li>\n<li class=\"publications-1\"><a href=\"http://www.alr-aerospace.ch/index.php?id=publications-1\" title=\"Publications\">Publications</a></li>\n<li class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.alr-aerospace.ch/index.php?id=links\" title=\"Links\">Links</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</nav>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t</header>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"intro\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"width\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"intro-content \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>ALR</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Arbeitsgruppe f\u00fcr Luft- und Raumfahrt <br>Groupe de D\u00e9veloppement de Projets A\u00e9rospatiaux <br>Aerospace Project Development Group <br></p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"body\" class=\"width\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section id=\"content\" class=\"one-column\">\n\t\t\t\t<article>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Centre of Competence in Air Traffic Management</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><em>Air Traffic Management is a crucial component of the air transport industry. ALR and our team of highly qualified experts offer a custom-made support in all fields of ATM. With the implementation of the Single European Sky II Programme of the European Commission, ATM organizations will be facing huge challenges to meet the performance criteria. We can assist you in identifying, planning and implementing the required actions.</em></p>\n<p><img alt=\"ATM Logo\" src=\"http://www.alr-aerospace.ch/images/ATM.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width: 539px;\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title2\"><strong>Main Activities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Airspace organization and management, civil-military co-operation, flexible use of airspace</li>\n\t<li>Safety and security management</li>\n\t<li>ATM safety investigations and reporting</li>\n\t<li>Flight Data Processing</li>\n\t<li>Air Traffic Flow and Capacity management</li>\n\t<li>Management of special events</li>\n\t<li>Project management</li>\n\t<li>Requirements engineering</li>\n\t<li>Technical support</li>\n\t<li>Basic and advanced training</li>\n\t<li>Human Resources Management</li>\n\t<li>Concept design</li>\n\t<li>Transition and change management</li>\n\t<li>Translation of specialized documents from or to German, English, French and Italian</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"title2\"><strong>Contact</strong></p>\n<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left: 20\">Carlo Bernasconi, senior ATM expert, member of the Performance Review Body of the Single European Sky<br />\n\t<br />\n\tPhone: +41 (0) 79 417 83 51<br />\n\tEmail: <a href=\"mailto:carlo.bernasconi@alr-aerospace.ch\">carlo.bernasconi@alr-aerospace.ch</a></p>\n<br />\n<p class=\"title2\"><strong>Description</strong></p>\n<p align=\"justify\">Established since 2008, ALR-ATM has successfully collaborated in international and national projects:</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li align=\"justify\">DMEAN (Dynamic Management of the European Airspace Network) with Eurocontrol</li>\n\t<li align=\"justify\">Design of the European Network Management Function with Eurocontrol</li>\n\t<li align=\"justify\">Training in ATM and airspace matters for EADS</li>\n\t<li align=\"justify\">Safety and security training for the Swiss Air Force.</li>\n</ul>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t</article>\n\t\t\t</section>\r\n        \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<footer>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-content width\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4>Navigate</h4>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li cla